categories: Category:Imperial Army officers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: Fhaen was a male officer of the Galactic Empire's Imperial Army. During the Galactic Civil War, Fhaen held the military rank of lieutenant and commanded a company of stormtroopers on New Valis fresh out of the Imperial Academy. Lieutenant Fhaen participated in the Rebel Alliance liberation of New Valis, where he and his forces were defeated by Rebel Marines.
